sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Super Admin, Admin, or Guard
    participant UI as JavaFX Profile Screen
    participant API as Spring Boot Profile API
    participant Service as UserService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Audit as AuditLogDAO

    User->>UI: Submit username or password change
    UI->>API: PUT /profile
    API->>Service: validate authenticated user and input
    Service->>DB: Check username uniqueness or current password
    Service->>DB: Update username or password_hash
    Service->>Audit: Write USER_UPDATED
    API-->>UI: Updated profile result
